Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.88,0:00:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,敌人？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.99,0:00:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,是坏人吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.56,0:00:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,不是坏不坏的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.52,0:00:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,教育机关可是邪教
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.76,0:00:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,嘴上说着要教育无知的愚民
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.49,0:00:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,却做着大屠杀之类的事情 一群疯子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.76,0:00:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,教育机关…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.13,0:00:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,已经察觉到了Empress吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.74,0:00:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,这也太快了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.56,0:00:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,要上吗 还是要逃命？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.18,0:00:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,那当然是逃...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.98,0:00:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,那家伙...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.13,0:00:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,喂！快起来！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.99,0:00:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.27,0:00:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,是教育机关！Empress已经过去了！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.22,0:00:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我们也追上去！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.90,0:00:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,啥啥啥？为啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.81,0:00:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,只能追上去了吧！跟上Empress！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.88,0:00:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,好...好的!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.60,0:00:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,混蛋...
